- input: "Task1 is a work-item.\nTask1 is assigned to Worker1.\nEvery work-item is a task.\nEvery task that is assigned to Worker1 is priority-task.\nEvery priority-task is queued.\nVerify that Task1 is queued."
  purpose: "Proof with relation-based rule chain."
  expect: "true"
- input: "Package1 is a package.\nPackage1 is delivered.\nEvery package that is delivered is verified.\nEvery package that is verified is archived.\nVerify that every package that is delivered is archived."
